text: Bahay Mo Ba 'To? () is a situational comedy series broadcast by GMA Network. Starring Wendell Ramos, it premiered on September 14, 2004 on the network's KiliTV line up. The series concluded on July 10, 2007 with a total of 148 episodes. ==Cast and characters== * Ronaldo Valdez as Nene Mulingtapang & Unyo * Wendell Ramos as Manny Boy Mulingtapang * Gladys Reyes as Kelly Mulingtapang * Bea Binene as Junabeth Mulingtapang * Gabriel Roxas as Julius Mulingtapang * Tessie Tomas as Baby Mulingtapang-Benoit & Anying * Pekto as Jonathan David Benoit * Sherilyn Reyes as Jessica Benoit * Sunshine Dizon as Dorothy Benoit * Jacob Chen as Raymond Benoit * Keempee de Leon as Harold Mangaluntoy * Francine Prieto as Jingle * Tiya Pusit as Bella * Dino Guevarra as Canor * Carlito Campos, Jr. as Mang Enriquez * Eva Papaya * Chynna Ortaleza ==Accolades== {| class="wikitable" |+ Accolades received by Bahay Mo Ba 'To? !
